OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,FAnyone who is feeling a bit lonely is
OL,7,Fbeing encouraged to go along to their
OL,8,Flocal Chatty Cafe where they are
OL,9,Fguarenteed a warm welcome as ITV
OL,10,FGranada's Elaine Willcox discovered.
OL,12,FAn ambitious project to help tackle
OL,13,Fthe loneliness epidemic is looking for
OL,14,Fnew venues and partners.
OL,16,FOne-in-four of us will experience
OL,17,Floneliness and feelings of isolation
OL,18,Fduring our life, which can feel even
OL,19,Fworse in the cold winter months along
OL,20,Fwith post Christmas blues.
