OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,FA new mum set out to change that when
OL,7,Fshe felt lonely for the first time,
OL,8,Flooking after her baby son who was one
OL,9,Fat the time.
OL,11,FAlex Hoskyn from Uppermill in Oldham,
OL,12,FGreater Manchester, said she came up
OL,13,Fwith the idea while on maternity leave
OL,14,Fin 2017, while she was in a cafe,
OL,15,Ffeeling "fed up and lonely".
OL,17,FShe set up a Chatty Cafe in Oldham to
OL,18,Fbring people together and the demand
OL,19,Fhas never been higher with more than
OL,20,F700 cafes taking part around the
OL,21,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
