OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,FThe scheme helps around 30,000 people
OL,7,Fwho said they felt isolated and lonely
OL,8,For just wanted some company.
OL,10,FAlex said: "There was an elderly lady
OL,11,Fon another table who looked really fed
OL,12,Fup and on another table was a guy with
OL,13,Fdisabilities with I think his carer.
OL,14,FThey were just looking around the
OL,15,Froom."
OL,17,F"It struck me in that moment, we could
OL,18,Fhave really helped each other if we'd
OL,19,Fbeen sat at one table."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
