OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,F"In our society it's a bit odd to just
OL,7,Fgo up to somebody so I didn't on that
OL,8,Fday, but it got me thinking about what
OL,9,Fcould have happened if we could have
OL,10,Fall chatted to each other."
OL,12,FAs a result, she started a website and
OL,13,Fposting on social media.
OL,15,FAlex said she was "amazed" when the
OL,16,Ffirst venues started to contact her,
OL,17,Fasking if they could support the idea.
OL,19,FSince then, the Chatty Cafe scheme has
OL,20,Fgrown to include 600 volunteers who
OL,21,Fsit at "chatter and natter" tables.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
