OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,FThere are also weekly online chatty
OL,7,Fcafes, which took off during the Covid-
OL,8,F19 pandemic.
OL,10,FOver the next five years, Alex said
OL,11,Fshe hoped to expand the scheme to
OL,12,F1,000 tables as well as raise #1m.
OL,14,F"We're a really small organisation but
OL,15,Fwe've got big ambitions," she
OL,16,Fexplained.
OL,18,F"We want to train more volunteers. The
OL,19,Fpublicity, the marketing - everything
OL,20,Fcosts money day-to-day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
