OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,F"Loneliness is an epidemic, it's a
OL,7,Fnational crisis and the more we can
OL,8,Fgive people the opportunity for face-
OL,9,Fto-face interaction the better."
OL,11,FAlex added: "After having my son,
OL,12,Fgoing into cafes and shops sometimes
OL,13,Fwas the only interaction you were
OL,14,Fhaving with other people that day.
OL,16,FIn the cafe today, it is all women,
OL,17,Fbut Alex says that is not always the
OL,18,Fcase.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
