OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,F"We've got volunteers and attendees
OL,7,Fall around the country who are men,
OL,8,Fwhich is great because men are
OL,10,Fnotoriously difficult to get to,
OL,11,Fespecially about loneliness."
OL,13,FI always say it kind of takes you from
OL,14,Ffeeling invisible to visible."
OL,16,FIn Great Sankey, near Warrington Jean
OL,17,FBooth saw an advert looking for
OL,18,Fvolunteers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
