OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,F"If it involves talking and drinking
OL,7,Ftea, I am the person to do that. So I
OL,8,Fwent through the training and here I
OL,9,Fam."
OL,11,F"We have one particular person that
OL,12,Fused to sit over on the side for a
OL,13,Flong time and gradually got encouraged
OL,14,Fto sit at our table, and it's made a
OL,15,Fhuge difference to that. That
OL,16,Fgentleman in particular."
OL,18,FAnd sometimes the chatting can go on
OL,19,Ffor quite some time, and it can be
OL,20,Fdifficult to close.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
