OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,F"There's always big smiles and very
OL,7,Freluctant to leave. Yeah, we we sort
OL,8,Fof have to push them out and say it's
OL,9,Fjust, you know."
OL,11,FKay Hughes says people may be a bit
OL,12,Fnervous about joining, but said it is
OL,13,Fworth joining a table.
OL,15,F"Don't be nervous about joining. It's
OL,16,Fa chat and natter. At the end of the
OL,17,Fday, you know, everybody's welcome.
OL,18,FYou know, you come in, you come in as
OL,19,Fa stranger, you go out with a friend."
