OL,3,CThe Chatty Cafe helps strangers make
OL,4,Cfriends
OL,6,FHaving her Ruby-coloured King Charles
OL,7,Fspaniel Ralphy has helped as an ice
OL,8,Fbreaker for new people joining the
OL,9,F'Chatty Table'.
OL,11,F"He's a complete icebreaker because
OL,12,Feverybody knows his name more than
OL,13,Fthey know my name.everybody expects me
OL,14,Fto come in with him, so it's nice."
OL,16,FStarting in Oldham there are now 720
OL,17,Fchatty cafes - with some supported by
OL,18,Flocal businesses allowing then to
OL,19,Fsubsidise the menu.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
