OL,6,FMarianne Penny, a barrista, chef and
OL,7,Fcrochet tutor at Stitch Station in
OL,8,FGreat Sankey said: "That's just magic,
OL,9,Fisn't it, hearing people join and hear
OL,10,Fthe conversations and laughter.
OL,12,F"It's great for us as well, to know
OL,13,Fthat we can provide that for people.
OL,15,F"We also get a little bit of
OL,16,Fsponsorship from the local co-op which
OL,17,Fis helpful because it helps reduce
OL,18,Fthose barriers for people on to that. "
